{"tid":874950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國當局截獲炸彈包裹, 寄往白宮、奧巴馬和希拉莉","createTime":"2018-10-24T14:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T17:30:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e2555f2c528ccefaba285e89a3dcd615661d96ee","tid":874950,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:45:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://wealth.hket.com/article/2192780/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2192780%2F&d=3l%2FvdMGQVhuJuhsOpjTboW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4891c067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://wealth.hket.com/article/2192780/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國當局截獲炸彈包裹 寄往白宮、奧巴馬和希拉莉<br />\n國際 22:33 2018/10/24<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國執法部門先後截獲多個可疑包裹，分別寄往白宮、前總統奧巴馬（Barack Obama）和前總統候選人希拉莉（Hillary Clinton），正就此展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞網絡（CNN）引述執法部門消息指，寄往白宮的可疑包裹內藏管狀炸彈，周三於首都華盛頓附近的基地截獲。該枚炸彈製造簡陋，但能夠引爆，近似著名投資者索羅斯（George Soros）日前收到的包裹。<br />\n<br />\n特勤局同日較早前表示，當局在本周初截獲兩個可疑包裹，分別寄給奧巴馬和希拉莉。當局表示，沒有人收到這些涉事包裹或因此面臨危險。"},{"pid":"a28e7d881c91df8367d85c41e720e2f1a7f4a4e5","tid":874950,"uid":161374,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"選舉，你明的"},{"pid":"631dea6c32ae180e3936cd2d9d4c811c90860cb6","tid":874950,"uid":99568,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:47:47.000Z","msg":"應該係民主黨專登咁做目標係假和比特朗普"},{"pid":"626a23716e6961d501e5c10ba6cdbf1dc76b9081","tid":874950,"uid":99568,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"應該係民主黨專登咁做目的係嫁禍畀特朗普"},{"pid":"43648773ed35a8ac11766916ad60f98c9244e23b","tid":874950,"uid":51620,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a28e7d881c91df8367d85c41e720e2f1a7f4a4e5","tid":874950,"uid":161374,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"選舉，你明的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T14:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但侵侵都有份"},